# Daily Habit Tracker Update Walkthrough

## New Features & Changes
### 1. Notification Toggle Fix 🐛
- **Issue**: "Turn On" button was showing "Failed: Notification permission denied".
- **Fixes**:
    - **Manifest**: Explicitly added `POST_NOTIFICATIONS` and `SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM` permissions to [AndroidManifest.xml](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml) (Required for Android 13+).
    - **Codebase**: Updated [utils.js](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js) to correctly handle Capacitor's 'display' permission status (handling `prompt` and `prompt_with_rationale` states).
    - **Build**: Used `npx vite build --debug` to ensure assets were correctly generated and refreshed.
- **Result**: "Turn On" should now correctly trigger the system permission dialog. If denied previously, you may need to clear app data or go to Settings to enable it manully.

### 2. Global Reset Implementation 🏆
- **Functionality**: "Reset All Data" now performs a complete factory reset.
- **Scope**:
    - Clears **ALL** habit history.
    - Resets theme to default (Pastel).
    - **IMPORTANT**: Clears "Perfect Day" count (Stats page will reset to 0).
    - Clears all local storage data.
- **Verification**: Verified code implementation in [App.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/App.jsx) and [Profile.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/Profile.jsx).

